Etymology. This species is dedicated to the memory of my beloved son Jonatán Iván Delgado Martinez (
1993–2014
) who left us too soon and so suddenly. My son, Jonatán, was a very cheerful, enthusiastic, passionate, friendly person; a tireless reader, poet, writer, composer, musician and rock drummer. You will always be in our hearts and we miss you immensely my beloved Jona.
